data.description: This home on 10 acres has been lovingly maintained with quality upgrades. 3 bedrooms & 2 baths on main floor plus full upstairs game room with Balcony for home office or game room with tons of built in storage . Hand scraped hickory flooring in main living areas . Jacuzzi tub , walk in shower , 6 skylights ,and 5 ceiling fans . Beautiful Japanese Garden with incredible Koi pond and waterfall . Sit on the back Aztek decking for the nature lover in you to take in the serene surroundings. A gardeners paradise awaits with vegetable garden area and a rose garden. Garage has extra cabinet storage and a climate controlled wine room. Steel roof , 2 storage sheds , all mil guard double paned windows and a 37gpm well ! Quick access to highway 80 and all manner of services
